Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.51,Madoka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.97,Tatsuya,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽~ 媽媽~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.85,Tatsuya,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上  早上了哦~
